## ‚ú® Features

### User Features

- **User Authentication**

  - User registration with encrypted passwords
  - Secure login/logout functionality
  - Session management

- **Movie Browsing**

  - Browse movies by categories (Action, Comedy, Drama, Documentary, Musical, Romance, Horror)
  - Search functionality to find specific movies
  - View detailed movie information (description, trailer, year, genre, price)
  - Embedded YouTube trailers

- **Shopping & Checkout**

  - Add movies to cart
  - Secure checkout process with payment simulation
  - Payment method selection (Credit/Debit Card)
  - Purchase receipts generation

- **Personal Library**

  - View purchased movies in personal library
  - Track spending and movie collection

- **User Account**
  - View account information
  - Track total money spent
  - See number of movies owned

### Admin Features

- **Dashboard**

  - Comprehensive overview of users, movies, and sales

- **User Management**

  - Add, edit, and delete users
  - View user information and purchase history
  - Generate user reports (PDF)
  - Track user expenses

- **Movie Management**

  - Add new movies to inventory
  - Edit movie details
  - Delete movies
  - Manage movie stock quantities
  - Bulk update movie inventory
  - Generate inventory reports (PDF)

- **Sales Management**

  - View all transactions
  - Edit sale information
  - Delete sales records
  - Generate sales reports (PDF)
  - View payment information
  - Generate total earnings reports

- **Reporting**
  - PDF report generation using TCPDF library
  - User view reports
  - User expense reports
  - Movie inventory reports
  - Sales reports
  - Payment information reports
  - Total revenue reports

## üõ†Ô∏è Technologies Used

- **Backend:** PHP 7.4+
- **Database:** MySQL/MariaDB
- **Frontend:** HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
- **Libraries:**
  - TCPDF for PDF generation
  - Font Awesome for icons
  - Bootstrap (admin panel)
- **Security:**
  - Prepared statements (SQL injection protection)
  - Password hashing (bcrypt)
  - Session management
  - Input validation
